com.interpss.dstab

Interface BaseDStabBus<TGen extends DStabGen,TLoad extends DStabLoad>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseAclfBus<TGen,TLoad>, BaseAcscBus<TGen,TLoad>, Bus, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAclfBus, IAclfBusAdaptation, IAclfBusAdjustment, IAclfBusFunc, IAclfBusZeroZFunc, IDynamicSimulation, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DStabBus
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseDStabBusImpl, DStabBusImpl

    public interface BaseDStabBus<TGen extends DStabGen,TLoad extends DStabLoad>
extends BaseAcscBus<TGen,TLoad>, IDynamicSimulation
    A representation of the model object 'DStab Bus'. Bus class for hosting bus stability study information.

    The following features are supported:

    • Init Load
    • Init Volt Mag
    • Load Model Switched
    • Freq
    • Bus Freq Measure Block
    • Dynamic Event
    • Info Only Dyn Model
    • Dynamic Bus Device List
    See Also:
    DstabPackage.getBaseDStabBus()

      • getInfoOnlyDynModel

        DynamicBusDevice getInfoOnlyDynModel()
        Returns the value of the 'Info Only Dyn Model' containment reference. Info only dynamic model is for define the composite load model, which itself does not fit the dynamicDevice concept, rather it is a "container" of static and dynamic devices/components. For composite load model (CMPLDW), it consists of an equivalent feeder model and several dynamic load components including three-phase induction motors, single-phase induction motor, ZIP loads. For more information, please refer to https://www.wecc.biz/Reliability/WECC%20Composite%20Load%20Model%20Specifications%2001-27-2015.docx
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Info Only Dyn Model' containment reference.
        See Also:
        setInfoOnlyDynModel(DynamicBusDevice), DstabPackage.getBaseDStabBus_InfoOnlyDynModel()
